—LLM。但只装大脑还不够。设想一个场景：</description></item><item><title>智能体时代：AI Agent的崛起与变革</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/05/ai%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91-%E7%AC%AC1%E7%AB%A0-%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/05/ai%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91-%E7%AC%AC1%E7%AB%A0-%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3/</guid><description><![CDATA[第1章 智能体时代：AI Agent的崛起与变革 当大语言模型从&quot;会聊天的程序&quot;进化为&quot;会做事的智能体&quot;，]]></description></item><item><title>从零实现ReAct Agent：手写思考-行动循环的智能体</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0react-agent%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A8%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>Simon Chen</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0react-agent%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A8%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93/</guid><description>什么是ReAct Agent？ 大多数现代AI智能体（ChatGPT、Claude、Copilot等）底层都运行着一个核心模式：思考→行动→观察</description></item><item><title>用CrewAI构建多智能体协作系统：让多个Agent协同完成复杂任务</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E7%94%A8crewai%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%9A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AAagent%E5%8D%8F%E5%90%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>Simon Chen</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E7%94%A8crewai%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%9A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AAagent%E5%8D%8F%E5%90%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1/</guid><description>为什么需要多智能体？ 一个Agent能回答问题、调用工具，但面对复杂任务时力不从心： 写一篇深度技术文章：需要调研、写大纲、写正文、审校 做竞品分</description></item><item><title>LangChain + ChromaDB 实战：构建本地知识库 RAG 问答系统</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/12/langchain-chromadb-rag-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/12/langchain-chromadb-rag-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description>前言 大语言模型（LLM）虽然强大，但存在两个核心痛点：知识截断和幻觉问题。模型的训练数据有截止日期，且无法准确回答其训练数据之外的问题。RA</description></item><item><title>用Python+LangChain从零搭建RAG系统：让大模型读懂你的私有文档</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/11/rag%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/11/rag%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/</guid><description>为什么需要RAG？ 大语言模型（LLM）虽然强大，但它有一个致命短板——知识截止日期。ChatGPT不知道你公司上周发布的内部文档，Claud</description></item><item><title>使用LangChain与ChromaDB构建本地知识库RAG问答系统</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/10/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8langchain%E4%B8%8Echromadb%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93rag%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/10/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8langchain%E4%B8%8Echromadb%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93rag%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description>前言 在大模型应用开发中，RAG（Retrieval-Augmented Generation，检索增强生成）是最核心的技术范式之一。它通过将外</description></item></channel></rss>